Maybe do the splitting with regex and in a general method?
Parser method:
```ts
private parseSpecialTag(text: string): {text: string, tag: string, value: string} | undefined {
   const match = /^(.*)\[(\w*):(\w*)\]$/.exec(text);
   return match
      ? { text: match[1], tag: match[2], value: match[3] }
      : undefined;
}
```
